2004-01-30    <Ulrich.Kuester@uni-jena.de>

	*  New Feature/Bugfix: When merging reports so far a
	translation of the coordinate systems of the different
	reports/factions has only been performed for level 0, the
	normal world, but NOT for level 1, the astral space.
	However, the coordinate systems of astral space are
	independent of those of normal space, thus such a trans-
	lation is necessary. It is now performed, too.
	
